WEBVTT

00:08.567 --> 00:10.872
Hey, Mike,
it's Rachel.

00:10.873 --> 00:12.140
I know I shouldn't
be doing this.

00:12.208 --> 00:13.475
I know you're seeing Jenny,

00:13.542 --> 00:15.477
but I can't stop thinking
about the kiss,

00:15.544 --> 00:17.812
and I can't go back.

